{"tid":800391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普警告世貿組織好好表現 否則美國將退出","createTime":"2018-08-30T23:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T06:53:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":104,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"7858aca2332d7e0a2037effb965dcec557c841ed","tid":800391,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T23:56:43.000Z","msg":"川普警告世貿組織好好表現 否則美國將退出<br />\n<br />\n2018-08-31 05:44<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕美國總統川普今天接受彭博（Bloomberg）專訪時，持續批評世界貿易組織（WTO），並揚言若是世貿組織再不好好表現，他會考慮讓美國退出這個組織。<br />\n路透社報導，美國若真退出世貿組織，恐將破壞現代全球貿易體系的主要基礎之一，而美國曾在創建這套體系扮演要角。<br />\n<br />\n川普說：「如果他們不好好表現，我會退出世貿組織。」<br />\n他曾抱怨美國在全球貿易上受到不公平待遇，並怪罪世貿組織容許這種情況出現。他也曾警告過可能對世貿組織採取行動，只是沒有明說會是什麼方式。<br />\n &lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"620b9b4a7c8df96050bf3e1098af4f3b97e7d279","tid":800391,"uid":141151,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:01:40.000Z","msg":"一係用23條踢贏国走<br />\n一係美國自己走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dc7afbed7f4f0f4ef2a18a990fd28f7136632f","tid":800391,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff793e015a09b06e3869c462b8cf396d67b2327","tid":800391,"uid":50457,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:08:57.000Z","msg":"中國最惠國待遇， bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016b7e52ff4ac43912da3f58948b62302aa7916a","tid":800391,"uid":35790,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:12:13.000Z","msg":"中國入世時承諾有幾多未兌現？"},{"pid":"de428945307874017cebe4a6dadd334a3f651e18","tid":800391,"uid":79563,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T00:13:08.000Z","msg":"美國退出W